race.comment: BOTH BOWERS ACE (8) boasts a consistent overall record including 29 wins from 113 starts, the latest hitting the minor money when third (29.98) over 520m at this track. Form here at the trip sound including 13 wins. Boxed wide but will go close with the right run. SPEEDY PIE (4) turned in a solid run last start over 520m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (30.15). Solid record here at the distance winning eight races. The form out of her last race has been franked. In the mix. REMA'S AMETHYST (7) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (23.31) last time in a NG at Richmond. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Bold showing expected. ZIPPING MOONEY (1) hit the frame here last start so don't underestimate.
